Features: Seat & Back formed from rounded steel tubes 19 mm and injected moulded flexible polyurethane.
Side made of steel tube with pressed steel sheet feet.
Armrest made of a bended steel sheet padded from both sides with polyurethane.
The top of the arm-rests are provided with an integral skin injected black polyurethane.
Seat and back fully upholstered.
Note: Each row requires one auditorium chair end side.
